<demos>

<name>TOAST</name>
<type>toolbox</type>
<icon>html/toast_logo_100.jpg</icon>
<description>
The TOAST toolbox is a collection of functions and scripts
for image reconstruction in optical diffusion imaging (ODT).
It contains a finite element solver (FEM) for modelling
diffuse light transport in scattering media that can be applied
to two- and three-dimensional problems.
Inverse solvers include nonlinear conjugate gradient as well
as Newton-type solvers for iterative minimisation of a cost
functional.
</description>

